<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='869370' id='t-869370'>we need to work for gender equality.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='871766' id='t-871766'>We cannot only train women
but forget about the men,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='875496' id='t-875496'>because the men are the real people
